About us
Welcome to Salty’s, the ultimate waterside hangout in Key Largo! Come check out our delicious food, refreshing drinks, and exciting games all in one place. It’s the perfect spot to relax, unwind, and have a blast together.
So, grab your cues and aim for victory on the pool table, test your accuracy with some darts, and let's create unforgettable memories at Salty's.
At Salty's, we take pride in offering a wide selection of beverages, including our specially crafted beer from the Islamorada Beer Company. Our collaboration with the renowned local brewery brings you the exclusive Islamorada Beer Company Salty's brew.
Get ready for an amazing time at Salty's! The staff is super friendly, the music is pumping, and the vibe is casual and laid-back. We can't wait to welcome you and make your visit one to remember. Join us at Salty's for a fun-filled evening of great food, refreshing drinks, and a fantastic ambiance. See you soon!
